name: CHAINED CONSUMER PRICE INDEX - All item data
desription: "The Chained Consumer Price Index for All Urban Consumers
agency_name: was introduced with the release of July data in August 2002.  Designated the C-CPI-U
url: the index supplements the existing Consumer Price Indexes already produced by the BLS: the CPI for All Urban Consumers (CPI-U) and the CPI for Urban Wage Earners and Clerical Workers (CPI-W)."
